{
  "texts": [
    "As one participant cautioned, \"if a student, for example, submits a written essay... students will struggle because arrmmm they'll only have that arrmm superficial surface learning.\"",
    "Furthermore, participants observed that ChatGPT might inadvertently lead to a surface-level understanding of the material, as it provides information without necessarily guiding students to critically evaluate what they read.",
    "The consensus among participants was that ChatGPT should be considered a supplementary tool to enhance the learning process rather than a complete replacement for traditional education.",
    "As a participant noted that:",
    "\"ChatGPT should be used as a tool for augmenting the learning process rather than replacing it entirely as a means of education.\""
  ]
}